{{Episode|2|The Great Swordsman Appears! Pirate Hunter Roronoa Zoro|Daikengō Arawaru! Kaizokugari Roronoa Zoro|大剣豪現る！海賊狩りロロノア・ゾロ|November 17|1999|Luffy and Koby arrive at Shell Island, a Marine base. They meet the bounty hunter Roronoa Zoro, held under arrest by the infamous marine, Captain Morgan, and his son Helmeppo.}}
{{Episode|3|Morgan vs. Luffy! Who's This Mysterious Beautiful Young Girl?|Mōgan tai Rufi! Nazo no Bishōjo wa Dare?|モーガンVSルフィ！謎の美少女は誰？|November 24|1999|Luffy convinces Zoro to join his crew, but they must first defeat Captain Morgan. After freeing the island from Morgan's oppressive rule, Koby is accepted as a marine while the other two continue on their journey.}}
