{{Episode|15|Defeat Kuro! Usopp's Tear-filled Determination!|Kuro o taose! Otoko Usoppu namida no ketsui!|クロを倒せ！男ウソップ涙の決意！|February 23|2000|Zoro and Buchi (of the Nyaban Brothers) face off once again as Luffy and Kuro begin their fight. Usopp orders the Usopp Pirates to run away with Kaya, but Jango goes after them. A flashback reveals how Captain Kuro faked his death with Captain Morgan and how he became Kaya's butler.}}
