{{Episode|17|Completely Infuriated! Kuro vs. Luffy, Final Battle!|Ikari bakuhatsu! Kuro vs Rufi kecchaku no yukue!|怒り爆発！クロVSルフィ決着の行方！|March 8|2000|Kuro's ultimate attack, "Shakushi", attacks everything in the area, whether friend or foe, and Luffy becomes enraged by his lack of regard for his crew. Will Luffy's determination overcome Kuro's sheer speed?}}
