{{Episode|38|Luffy in Trouble! Fishmen vs. Luffy Pirates!|Rufi Dai Pinchi! Gyojin vs Rufi kaizokudan|ルフィ大ピンチ！魚人VSルフィ海賊団|August 23|2000|The Straw Hats face the Fishmen themselves as the villagers watch from the sidelines.}}
